replies.body:
Some offhand comments about girls being pretty, and asking Shyvana out to lunch. So cute and wholesome, I love her. 
{{sticker:sg-lux}} 
Also, I'm glad someone at Riot confirmed it, otherwise part of the community would be gaslighting people who read her as a lesbian. It's nice to have a character in league who's 100% canonically confirmed to be LGBTQ+ for once. I hope they keep up the pace and maybe we get an asexual Fiora, or even some trans representation. ^_^
